    "body": "<!-- Thank you for your contribution! Please follow these guidelines to enhance your pull request. If anything is unclear, submit your PR and reach out to maintainers for assistance. Join our Slack community at https://slack.sglang.ai to discuss further. -->\r\n\r\n## Motivation\r\n\r\nSince the FI TRT-LLM backend was already added for blockscale MoE, add it for per-tensor FP8, specifically for Llama 4.\r\nOnly for SM100\r\n\r\n<!-- Describe the purpose and goals of this pull request. -->\r\n\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\nModify the apply code of MoE methods.\r\n\r\n> Generally I only used ModelOpt checkpoints, so I didn't add the code in the normal FP8 file.\r\n> There is some issues with ModelOpt loading on main, merge this in after https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/pull/10154\r\n\r\n<!-- Detail the changes made in this pull request. -->\r\n\r\n## Accuracy Tests\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n```\r\npython3 benchmark/gsm8k/bench_sglang.py --num-shots 8 --num-questions 1319 --parallel 200\r\nDownloading from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openai/grade-school-math/master/grade_school_math/data/test.jsonl to /tmp/test.jsonl\r\n/tmp/test.jsonl: 732kB [00:00, 33.3MB/s]                                                                                                                                                                                                          \r\n100%|█████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████| 1319/1319 [00:39<00:00, 33.54it/s]\r\nAccuracy: 0.935\r\nInvalid: 0.000\r\nLatency: 39.421 s\r\nOutput throughput: 3492.464 token/s\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\nI set parallel 50 due to some strange server issue on main w/ overlap scheduler, it's not related to this PR.\r\n```\r\npython3 benchmark/gsm8k/bench_sglang.py --num-shots 8 --num-questions 1319 --parallel 50\r\n100%|████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████| 1319/1319 [01:13<00:00, 17.95it/s]\r\nAccuracy: 0.931\r\nInvalid: 0.000\r\nLatency: 73.587 s\r\nOutput throughput: 1864.289 token/s\r\n```\r\n\r\n<!-- If this pull request affects model outputs (e.g., changes to the kernel or model forward code), provide accuracy test results. -->\r\n\r\n## Benchmarking and Profiling\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n```\r\npython -m sglang.launch_server \\\r\n  --model-path /mnt/external-quantized-models/models/nvidia__Llama-4-Maverick-17B-128E-Instruct-FP8 \\\r\n  --tp 8 \\\r\n  --attention-backend triton \\\r\n  --model-loader-extra-config '{\r\n    \"enable_multithread_load\": true,\r\n    \"num_threads\": 8\r\n  }' \\\r\n  --trust-remote-code \\\r\n  --moe-runner-backend triton \\\r\n  --quantization modelopt_fp8\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 8         \r\nSuccessful requests:                     64        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  53.09     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      65536     \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 65536     \r\nTotal input vision tokens:               0         \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  65536     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    65673     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.21      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          1234.33   \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         1234.33   \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          2468.67   \r\nConcurrency:                             8.00      \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   6632.70   \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 6634.04   \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          144.41    \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        143.07    \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           162.07    \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           6.34      \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         6.34      \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            6.74      \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            7.00      \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            16.29     \r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n```\r\npython -m sglang.launch_server \\\r\n  --model-path /mnt/external-quantized-models/models/nvidia__Llama-4-Maverick-17B-128E-Instruct-FP8 \\\r\n  --tp 8 \\\r\n  --attention-backend triton \\\r\n  --model-loader-extra-config '{\r\n    \"enable_multithread_load\": true,\r\n    \"num_threads\": 8\r\n  }' \\\r\n  --trust-remote-code \\\r\n  --moe-runner-backend flashinfer_trtllm \\\r\n  --quantization modelopt_fp8\r\n```\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 8         \r\nSuccessful requests:                     64        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  45.07     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      65536     \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 65536     \r\nTotal input vision tokens:               0         \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  65536     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    65692     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.42      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          1453.96   \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         1453.96   \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          2907.91   \r\nConcurrency:                             7.99      \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   5630.01   \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 5630.28   \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          146.01    \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        146.60    \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           169.93    \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           5.36      \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         5.35      \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            5.76      \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            5.99      \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            34.35     \r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\n<!-- If this pull request impacts inference speed, provide benchmarking and profiling results. -->\r\n\r\n| Metric | Before (`--moe-runner-backend triton`) | After (`--moe-runner-backend flashinfer_trtllm`) | Δ | % Change |\r\n|:--|--:|--:|--:|--:|\r\n| Request Throughput (req/s) | 1.21 | 1.42 | +0.21 | +17.4% |\r\n| Input Token Throughput (tok/s) | 1234.33 | 1453.96 | +219.63 | +17.8% |\r\n| Total Token Throughput (tok/s) | 2468.67 | 2907.91 | +439.24 | +17.8% |\r\n| Mean E2E Latency (ms) | 6632.70 | 5630.01 | −1002.69 | −15.1% |\r\n| Mean TTFT (ms) | 144.41 | 146.01 | +1.60 | +1.1% |\r\n| Mean ITL (ms) | 6.34 | 5.36 | −0.98 | −15.5% |\r\n",
